title: MisterMusic Show 380 - indie,alternative,rock,radio
description:
MisterMusic Show 380 -192kbps MP3 [2 hours]-


New music this week from The Belligerents, and Turin Brakes.
Plus the most successful single by a band, that hit the airwaves in November 1990 is the 'Oldie of the Week'.  It was a number 1 hit on the modern rock chart for 3 weeks that year.
Broadcasting weekly, and heard globally- it's The MisterMusic Show.

Listen to the MisterMusic Show on RockXS Radio
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

For recorded podcasts of the MisterMusic show, visit his podcast page-  
http://mistermusicshow.com/ . Shows are updated there first every Sunday.
Or you can google search mistermusicshow (spelled as one word) and you'll find it.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

MisterMusic is also a presenter on PodCloud1. The website that gives you shorter music segments and themes...easier 
to enjoy in the hectic schedules of today. Check it out- PodCloud1 'The One for Great Music' http://podcloud1.com/
